rComments: This prof is brand new and is in need of improvement. She reads her PPT and doesn't seem very passionate about the course. We had to write a paper about a specific scope of practice and she was a pretty good grader FOR SOME THINGS . However, her exams had a lot of errors and the questions were not clear. Very boring prof overall and avoid her!

Prof reads powerpoint in front of class and this class seemed to be her last priority. Hard to communicate with her and exams had mistakes. I recommend doing the lectures she asks to do since they do apply to the exams.
